'''Andrew George "Andy" Rankin''' (born 11 May 1945 in [[Bootle]]) is an English former [[professional]] [[association football|footballer]] who played in [[the Football League]] as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Everton F.C.|Everton]], [[Watford F.C.|Watford]] and [[Huddersfield Town F.C.|Huddersfield Town]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.neilbrown.newcastlefans.com/player/andyrankin.htm |title=Andy Rankin |work=UK A<U+2013>Z Transfers |publisher=Neil Brown |accessdate=3 October 2009}}</ref> In 1973 Rankin became the inaugural [[List of Watford F.C. Players of the Season|Watford Player of the Season]], an accolade he would reclaim in the 1974&ndash;75 season.<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.watfordfc.com/page/Awards/0,,10400~1034010,00.html|title=Players of the Season|accessdate=8 October 2009|publisher=Watford F.C}}</ref>

